# Quest: Power Goggles
betterquesting.quest.GvlZG9IESmW2qsEMw-hkIw.name=Power Goggles
betterquesting.quest.GvlZG9IESmW2qsEMw-hkIw.desc=Wanna see how your LSC is doing but don't want to run to it or your information panel every time? Get yourself a pair of §6§oPower Goggles§r to see your energy storage straight from the HUD!%n%nBy §adefault§r the goggles are §cunlinked§r and will monitor the amount of energy in your wireless network.%n%nTo link the goggles to an LSC, §cRight+Click§r the controller with the goggles in your hand. §cShift+Right Click§r air to unlink.%n%nIf you wish to move or modify the display you can do so by opening the power goggles config menu!%n%n[warn]Make sure to check your keybinds! There's also a keybind for toggling the power chart!%n%nOr, if you don't wanna deal with that, you can use the /powergoggles command[/warn]

