betterquesting.quest.AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAG6Q.name=Purchase Tier 1 Graphics Card
betterquesting.quest.AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAG6Q.desc=I'll sell you a Tier 1 Graphics Card for four Bitcoins.

