# Quest: Get Your Priorities Straight
betterquesting.quest.Hbq2zJcoQbWK20-2A-kI1Q.name=Get Your Priorities Straight
betterquesting.quest.Hbq2zJcoQbWK20-2A-kI1Q.desc=You might find yourself setting up complicated systems involving many storage buses with differing priorities. To make it less tedious, grab a priority card!%n%nThis tool allows you to set many buses to the same priority with a single click... but better yet, it also features §nincrement and decrement modes!§r Every time you click on a bus, the priority will be set to one higher/lower than the previous bus you clicked, so setting up large arrays of descending priorities is a breeze.

